Class ApiClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.services.openapi.apiclient.ApiClient

  • public final class ApiClient
extends Object
    Used by the OpenAPI VDM to access HTTP-related information, such as the target URL of the headers.
